---

<BaseLayout title="Board Portal">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
    <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-8">
      <div class="bg-yellow-50 border border-yellow-200 rounded-lg p-6 mb-6">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-yellow-900 mb-2">Restricted Access</h2>
        <p class="text-yellow-800">
          This area is restricted to board members only. Authentication and authorization 
          will be implemented in a future update.
        </p>
      </div>

      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">Board Portal</h1>
      <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
        Welcome to the board portal. This area will contain board-only resources and tools.
      </p>

      <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-lg p-6">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">Coming Soon</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
          The following features are planned for the board portal:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-700 space-y-2 ml-4">
          <li>Secure document management</li>
          <li>Resident directory</li>
          <li>Maintenance request tracking</li>
          <li>Financial reports and statements</li>
          <li>Voting and survey tools</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-6 p-4 bg-blue-50 border border-blue-200 rounded-lg">
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-700">
          <strong>Note:</strong> This page is currently accessible to all visitors. 
          Authentication and access control will be added in a future update.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
